title: Golf-Bland and Fitzpatrick set pace at Wentworth
text:
May 24, 2018 / 1:00 PM / Updated 8 hours ago Golf-Bland and Fitzpatrick set pace at Wentworth Reuters Staff 2 Min Read
LONDON, May 24 (Reuters) - England’s Richard Bland made the most of ideal conditions to set the early pace at BMW PGA Championship at Wentworth on Thursday, carding a five-under 67 to top the leaderboard.
